      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or dents, and the interior remains in pristine condition, still smelling like new. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine runs silently, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and every electronic feature works exactly as intended. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
