      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is a fantastic opportunity for someone looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper with plenty of potential. While it requires some mechanical and cosmetic TLC, it's a great foundation for a restoration project or a reliable source of parts. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
